## **What is Social Bookmarking in SEO?**  
Social bookmarking is the process of submitting your website links to online bookmarking platforms. It helps in:  
✔ **Faster Indexing:** Search engines crawl bookmarked links quickly.  
✔ **High-Quality Backlinks:** Many bookmarking sites provide DoFollow links.  
✔ **Referral Traffic:** These sites can drive real users to your website.  
✔ **Improved Domain Authority:** Quality backlinks improve your site's SEO score.  

If done correctly, **social bookmarking in SEO** can **boost website traffic** and **enhance search engine ranking**.  

