## **FAQs (Frequently Asked Questions)**  

### **Q1: Are social bookmarking backlinks good for SEO?**  
Yes! They help with **faster indexing, authority building, and referral traffic**.  

### **Q2: How many social bookmarking sites should I use?**  
Use **10-15 high-quality sites** instead of 100+ low DA sites.  

### **Q3: Are social bookmarking sites still effective in 2025?**  
Yes! **Google still values** bookmarking backlinks if done **organically & naturally**.  

### **Q4: Which social bookmarking sites provide DoFollow links?**  
Some great **DoFollow bookmarking sites** include **RightBookmarking, Scoop.it, DZone, and Folkd**.  

